juan cordon page 1 juan cordon juan cordon is the food service director for the santa clara unified school district he has over 22 years of large volume food service management experience he has worked for some of the largest food service companies in the world including marriott sodexho lsg sky chefs and aramark juan has spent over 14 years working or consulting with schools to improve their food service operations he has a bs degree in hotel and restaurant management from golden gate university but most of his knowledge comes from his hands on approach to food service juan is a father of 3 school aged children which has changed the way he sees his role in schools he is committed to providing better healthier food in schools and is always searching for innovative ideas to accomplish this goal his approach to schools food service is simple buy real food have people who are trained prepare it and then serve it with a smile
